        <abstract>
            <p>Thanks RM for his paper on mimicry.</p>
            <p>Cannot answer RM’s query because he believes it impossible to define large variations.</p>
            <p>Believes monstrosities are generally injurious and are not often, if ever, taken advantage of in nature.</p>
        </abstract>
